1
00:00:00,075 --> 00:00:01,337
In this lecture on Docker

2
00:00:01,775 --> 00:00:05,325
we will explore the core concepts and architecture of Docker

3
00:00:05,750 --> 00:00:08,875
an essential tool for modern software development and deployment

4
00:00:09,262 --> 00:00:12,725
Docker is a platform designed to facilitate the creation

5
00:00:12,988 --> 00:00:13,637
deployment

6
00:00:13,875 --> 00:00:16,438
and execution of applications using containers

7
00:00:16,825 --> 00:00:22,075
Containers provide a lightweight and efficient alternative to traditional virtual machines

8
