9
00:00:29,387 --> 00:00:33,237
The lecture will cover how Docker streamlines the development process

10
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:35,013
enhances collaboration

11
00:00:35,413 --> 00:00:39,112
and simplifies the deployment of applications across different environments

